{"tid":1164600,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"奧地利Salzburg行程求狠批","createTime":"2019-05-21T08:20:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T13:52:20.000Z","uid":3560,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"71d43fbf035d63bb55bc8ca8f44848d103fd1a52","tid":1164600,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T08:20:11.000Z","msg":"話說琴晚見到Salzburg Festival有兩場音樂會好想睇剩番最後一張飛諗都無諗就買咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後而家就要諗買機票去幾耐去邊度<br />\n機票酒店乜柒都未book <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔太熟歐洲，draft咗個行程求狠批：<br />\n24 Aug HK-Munich （飛慕尼黑好似近過維也納，飛qatar定emirates好？）<br />\n25 Aug Munich<br />\n26 Aug Salzburg （晚上睇音樂會）<br />\n27 Aug Salzburg<br />\n28 Aug Golling ／Bluntauseen（宿一晚）<br />\n29 Aug Golling ／Bluntauseen，夜晚返Salzburg<br />\n30 Aug Salzburg （早上睇音樂會），下午去Hallstatt，Hallstatt宿一夜<br />\n31 Aug Hallstatt，諗緊Hallstatt宿多晚好定轉去Obertraun好<br />\n中間未諗到<br />\n1-3 Sep 去Linz好唔好，未諗<br />\n3-6 Sep Vienna，5號去睇歌劇，6 Sep Vienna走<br />\n<br />\n其實好多年前已經曾經去過一日Salzburg同兩日維也納，嗰啲咩莫扎特博物館維也納公園同Salzburg Castle其實已經去過曬了，但當年天氣好差，所以再去又可以 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以都係諗緊主要係睇音樂會同風景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d14174e95902ff29249d98e9ca4b29c42fbacb2","tid":1164600,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T08:30:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62079c9471d4f7fb79ef4d0f9b1cca17ee0336c7","tid":1164600,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T09:27:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmo